snippet.textDisplay: I was just smitten by the composition me n my wife from last night already listened more than 50 times and each time found something new. The every tone of rubab from sazz the bass line percussion fingertip midi controllers seaboard sync everything is superb. Hats off to the bass player who has done miraculously well with this composition from beginning with base cutoffs and taking the charge again. Man he is the real king of composition and showed why he can do things simply better than other. Just listen to the music in q dolby atmos environment or in airpod u will justify what I said is absolutely true dear.
